Part three of this illuminating series exploring the music business from behind
the scenes takes a look at PR, the unseen force behind all the biggest musical
acts in the world. With unique revelations, unseen footage and unrivalled access,
it tells the story of the rise of PR within the music industry through the eyes of
the people who lived it. Highlights include the PR campaigns behind superstars
Jimi Hendrix, Taylor Swift and David Bowie.

Narrated by PR Alan Edwards
